The '''Portmaster's Pavilion''' was a building thirty meters wide that once stood in [[Redhaven]]'s spaceport on [[Rhommamool/Legends|Rhommamool]]. After [[Nom Anor]] came to power, it was torn down to create the center of the [[Square of Hopeful Redemption]].

